description: The anemic floral decor of the cottage is washed in silvered light that streams through a glass-paned bay window.  A mild brume hangs heavy in the air, nearly obscuring some provincial elm cabinetry that fully lines the back wall.  Herb-filled baskets and vials of oil are strewn about a flat-topped cypress tree stump, serving as a workspace.
title: [A Stony Cottage]
